      <p>We may update these terms from time to time. Continued use of the site constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-ink">Contact</h2>
      <p>Questions about these terms? Visit our <a href="/contact" class="text-link underline-offset-4 hover:underline">Contact</a> page.</p>
    </div>

    <a href="/playables" class="mt-10 inline-block text-sm text-link underline-offset-4 hover:underline">← Back to playables</a>
  </main>
</Layout>
